                <note rend="inline" type="source">781.003/276h: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Diplomatic Agent and Consul General at Tangier</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Blake</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-09-06T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 6, 1939—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>12. Has Childs arrived? If so, has he been able to ascertain whether Marchal
                    still plans to commence negotiations this autumn or whether they are likely to
                    be indefinitely postponed?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
